53:01.000 --> 53:05.000
He was saying maybe we're going to have another war and peace here. So he had to chop it down.

53:05.000 --> 53:12.000
And what he was trying to depict, it was a very level on the first burn that they did in a dock fashion.

53:12.000 --> 53:19.000
