53:19.000 --> 53:24.000
And when you fired trying to translate, it would rotate the whole stack.

53:24.000 --> 53:27.000
And when you tried to translate or rotate it would translate.

53:27.000 --> 53:33.000
So they had to figure out new controls, a little bit like Revenger, head and panacea stomach or vice versa.

53:33.000 --> 53:36.000
Yes, so what you saw in the movie was digging the first burn.

53:36.000 --> 53:44.000
It was more of a composite of all three major burns that we did, but more like the first one.

53:44.000 --> 53:52.000
And so they got that learning curve, the crew got that learning curve down later, where they were actually pretty comfortable in doing this.

53:52.000 --> 54:01.000
And I think Fred Hayes control role and swagger time the engine burn and level handle pitch.

54:01.000 --> 54:06.000
