They actually targeted the overburden there, which brought us in a bit short, which brought us closer to the carrier than we had been previously.

54:52.000 --> 54:55.000
It was close. It was within eyesight of the carrier.

54:55.000 --> 54:57.000
It was two miles, two to five miles.

54:57.000 --> 54:58.000
Thank you.

